OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Mon 11 May to Wed 20 May
OL,6,FChangeable and at times rather
OL,7,Funsettled conditions look to dominate
OL,8,Fthrough the middle part of May, with
OL,9,Flow pressure often close by. This
OL,10,Fmeans periods of rain or showers, some
OL,11,Fof which could be heavy, for many
OL,12,Fplaces, though some drier interludes
OL,13,Fare also expected. For the most part,
OL,14,Ftemperatures are likely to be close to
OL,15,For perhaps a little below normal,
OL,16,Fthough depending on the position of
OL,17,Flow pressure relative to the UK, there
OL,18,Fis the chance of brief warmer mroe
OL,19,Fhumid interludes extending north from
OL,20,Fthe near continent. With this would be
OL,21,Fthe chance of some thunderstorms,
OL,22,Fthese most likely affecting parts of
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,23,FEngland and Wales.
